ParaFun

public ParaFun(Pos pos,

               java.lang.String name,
               java.util.List<VarDecl> decls,

Constructs a new ParaFun object.

Parameters:
pos - - the original position in the file
path - - a valid path to the Unit containing this paragraph (can be "" if it's the main unit)
name - - the name of the paragraph (it cannot be "")
decls - - the list of parameters
type - - the return type (null if this is a predicate rather than a function)
value - - the body of the predicate/function
Throws:
ErrorSyntax - if the path contains '@'
ErrorSyntax - if the name contains '@' or '/'
ErrorSyntax - if the name is equal to "", "none", "iden", "univ", or "Int"
ErrorSyntax - if decls contains duplicate names
ErrorInternal - if pos==null, path==null, name==null, decls==null, or value==null
